&lt;li&gt;In-depth knowledge of ICD-10, CPT, and HCPCS coding systems, medical terminology, anatomy and physiology, and healthcare CMS/payer specific documentation requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and accuracy in coding and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated computer literacy and ability to efficiently navigate Electronic Medical Records (EMR) systems&lt;/li&gt;
