&lt;p&gt;Metro Vein Centers is seeking an experienced Network Engineer to lead the design, implementation, and ongoing management of our network infrastructure across 70+ clinic and corporate locations. This is a newly created role driven by our strategic initiative to modernize network architecture, improve internet reliability, and transition toward a cloud-first, zero trust security model.&lt;/p&gt;
